flowchart TD
    A["CGEventTap receives key event"] --> B{"capture_enabled?"}
    B -->|No| Z["Return original event"]
    B -->|Yes| C{"debug passthrough combo?"}
    C -->|Yes| Z
    C -->|No| D{"Probe pending?"}

    D -->|Yes, different keycode| E{"Event is non-mod and non-functional?"}
    E -->|Yes| F["Pass through to OS\nDo not queue/return app event"]
    E -->|No| G["Consume event\nDo not queue/return app event"]
    F --> H["Wait for probe lock or timeout"]
    G --> H

    D -->|No or same keycode| I{"Event type"}

    I -->|KeyDown| J{"Modifier or functional?"}
    J -->|Yes| K["Consume\nQueue normal event with preset alias"]
    J -->|No| L{"Alias already locked?"}

    L -->|No| M["Start probe (pending keycode + start time)\nDebug: probe_start"]
    M --> N["Pass through to OS\nTrack key internally as deferred"]
    N --> H

    L -->|Yes| O["Pass through to OS\nQueue KeyDown with locked alias"]

    I -->|KeyUp| P{"Modifier or functional?"}
    P -->|Yes| Q["Consume\nQueue KeyUp"]
    P -->|No| R{"Deferred unresolved key?"}
    R -->|Yes| S["Pass through to OS\nNo queued app event"]
    R -->|No| T["Pass through to OS\nQueue KeyUp"]

    I -->|FlagsChanged| U["Update modifier/fn state\nQueue ModChanged\nConsume"]

    H --> V{"Probe lock received from SDL keydown alias?"}
    V -->|Yes| W["Lock alias mapping\nBackfill queued/current state\nEmit deferred KeyDown if still held\nDebug: probe_locked"]
    V -->|No| X{"Probe age >= 4ms?"}
    X -->|Yes| Y["Drop unresolved probe key\nClear pending probe\nDebug: probe_timeout_drop"]
    X -->|No| H

    O --> AA["Return/queue available to main"]
    K --> AA
    Q --> AA
    T --> AA
    U --> AA
    W --> AA
